- Active alerts indicate ongoing issues that have not been resolved or are still being addressed;
- The query focuses on the most recent data to ensure the latest network conditions are being monitored;
- The results are ordered to highlight the most severe issues first, where higher values of mean network delay and mean response time are considered more critical.

